1. *Majka* je mnogo dragocena osoba. (Mother is a very precious person.)
2. *Majka* je uvek bila tu za mene. (Mother was always there for me.)
3. Moju *majku* veoma cenim. (I highly value my mother.)
4. *Majčina* ljubav je neprocenjiva. (Mother's love is priceless.)
5. Uvek ću se ponašati kako bih ugodio *majci*. (I will always behave in order to please my mother.)
6. *Majčin* glas me uvek utišava. (My mother's voice always calms me down.)